description:
DC is on a promo tour (Almost Christmas in theaters now!), Karlous is on the road and Clayton came from the airport to the studio with Navv Green, Will Foskey and EDuchess to discuss the election results. We're out of the trap and in the studio helping our 85 South Show audience prepare for the new change of power. Download, subscribe and share! #85SouthShow #ThisPodcastIsFor
